headline: This Stock Wins Three Feathers In Its Cap After 137% Gain
summary: Third, Emcor stock has also snatched a spot on the elite IBD 50 index.  The stock pulled back gently and resumed its advance after that earnings report.  The rally helped the stock rise past a profit zone to an all-time high of 532.38 on Nov. 21, according to IBD MarketSurge.
